Hiking Buddy: A social media app to find information on hikes and find a group to hike with!




Hiking Buddy Stories
  
  -User can see hikes in their area and click on them
  -When clicked on information about the hike will show up like difficulty, length, weather conditions, trail conditions (Most info will be crowd sourced through reviewing a hike)
  -Users can join a group on a hike
  -Users can review hikes
  -Users can post to their profile about their hikes (Pictures, Videos, and Text)
  -Users must make a profile and sign in

Hiking Buddy Views
  -Login Page
  -Find a Hike Page
  -Home Page
  -Hike Info Page
  -Hike Review Page
  -Profile Page
